    "text": "# lensing.py\nlensing_py = '''\nimport numpy as np\n\n_G = 6.67430e-11\n_c = 299792458.0\n\ndef deflection_angle(M, b, gamma_X=1.0):\n \"\"\"\n 近似偏折角： α ≈ (1+γ_X) 4GM/(b c^2)\n - M: 质量(kg)\n - b: 决定冲量参数(m)\n - gamma_X: 与 GR 的 PPN 参数 γ 类似（教学用）\n 返回弧度。\n \"\"\"\n return (1.0 + gamma_X) * 4.0*_G*M/(b*_c*_c)\n\ndef shapiro_delay(M, r1, r2, b, gamma_X=1.0):\n \"\"\"\n 简化的 Shapiro 延迟估算（对数项近似）；仅演示接口，非严谨工程版。\n \"\"\"\n L = max((r1*r1 + r2*r2 - b*b), 1e-12)**0.5\n pref = (1.0 + gamma_X) * 2.0*_G*M/(_c**3)\n arg = (r1 + r2 + L) / max((r1 + r2 - L), 1e-12)\n return pref * np.log(arg)\n'''\nopen(f\"{base}/src/xingphysics/lensing.py\",\"w\").write(lensing_py)"
