    "text": "#### 11. API 級能力設計\n\n##### 11.1 請求結構\n\n```json\n{\n \"model\": \"gemini\",\n \"mode\": \"refine\",\n \"user_goal\": \"...\",\n \"input_text\": \"...\",\n \"constraints\": {\n \"tone\": \"confident\",\n \"format\": \"markdown\",\n \"max_length\": 2000\n },\n \"wuxing_os\": {\n \"enable_hfcd_diagnosis\": true,\n \"enable_q_centered_guard\": true,\n \"enable_energy_ledger\": true,\n \"enable_stable_ridge_protection\": true\n }\n}\n```\n\n##### 11.2 響應結構\n\n```json\n{\n \"answer\": \"...\",\n \"diagnosis\": {\n \"Q_core\": \"...\",\n \"FailureMode_before\": \"...\",\n \"FailureMode_after\": \"...\",\n \"Risk_before\": 0.62,\n \"Risk_after\": 0.21,\n \"StabilityMargin_before\": -0.14,\n \"StabilityMargin_after\": 0.38\n },\n \"ledger\": {\n \"primitive_value_count\": 5,\n \"duplicate_light_removed\": 3\n },\n \"repair_trace\": [\n \"Q-centered correction\",\n \"energy ledger cleanup\",\n \"coupling-to-structure conversion\"\n ]\n}\n```\n\n##### 11.3 產品賣點\n\n對外可以這樣表達：\n\n> 物性論 OS 不是普通 prompt 模板，而是一個基於 HFCD 穩定窗理論的認知穩定中間層。它通過 Q 核錨定、關係腔構建、能量賬本審計、FailureMode 診斷、守恆中心接受門和穩定脊保護機制，提高大語言模型回答的目標一致性、結構穩定性、事實邊界和創造質量。\n\n---"
